							<div style="width: 230px; float: left; position: relative;">
								<a href="site.do?siteId=174">Are Public Investment Efficient in Creating Capital Stocks in Developing Countries? Estimates of Government Net Capital Stocks for 26 Developing Countries, 1970-2002 </a><br/>
								<div class="loupe">
									<a href="#abstractPaper-174" rel="abstractPaper174" title="Details of the article">
										<img alt="" src="images/icones/loupe.gif" />
