							<div style="width: 230px; float: left; position: relative;">
								<a href="site.do?siteId=81">Currency Crises Early Warning Systems: why they should be Dynamic</a><br/>
								<div class="loupe">
									<a href="#abstractPaper-81" rel="abstractPaper81" title="Details of the article">
										<img alt="" src="images/icones/loupe.gif" />
